{"tid":2205002,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"遭轟整型怪物！百萬網紅隆胸紀錄「A到E」乳量激增超震撼","createTime":"2020-09-16T12:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:28:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05481080c990d3613cd1411b62bd0b75b455adb8","tid":2205002,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:57:53.000Z","msg":"隨著科技進步，不少人會透過整型來讓自己變得更美，藉此提升自己的自信，南韓就出現一名20歲網紅趙秀珍，年紀輕輕，全身上下就已多次動刀，引來外界關注。近日，她更大方上傳自己隆胸後的成果影片，不料卻湧入網友們眾多負評，讓她終於決定暫時停止整型一事。<br />\n<br />\n趙秀珍雖然只有20歲，但愛美的她，已在過去一年內動了雙眼皮，隆鼻和全身抽脂等手術，成功從原本清秀的少女，變身成五官精緻的網紅臉。她也毫不避諱的大方公開自己整形前後的對比照，甚至拍成影片放上網路，每支影片目前都有破百萬的點閱，看起來相當受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n近日，她跑去隆胸，直接從原本的A罩杯升級成E罩杯，但似乎是身體突然出現大幅變化的關係，體內放了太多假體，讓趙秀珍透露，手術結束18天還是很痛，通常一般人只要3天就可以恢復得差不多，但她仍大方在鏡頭前，大方秀出隆胸後的成果，看起來相當驚人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說愛美的人沒有錯，但趙秀珍在短時間內，安排了這麼多的整型手術，開始引來各方爭議，有網友就表示她根本是整型成隱，甚至叫她「整型怪物」，不過也有人誇讚變美了，但還是希望她不要忘記，真正的自信是不要忘了自己。趙秀珍也發現，好像對自己太壞了，接下來1到2年內，將會停止整型，好好休息。"},{"pid":"2ad56c78b499a47cfb68cb7c3897c0f4ccf47c49","tid":2205002,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773773-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773773-PH.jpg&h=8a109cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲趙秀珍歷經多次整型，已經有了一張精緻臉蛋。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773778-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773778-PH.jpg&h=a9311b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773776-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773776-PH.jpg&h=fb47309c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲趙秀珍常大方公開自己整型前後的對比照。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773777-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773777-PH.jpg&h=3ac9ef5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲趙秀珍和年幼時期的模樣幾乎是完全不同。（圖／翻攝自IG）"},{"pid":"a063f81ab2c4d23d8b0685d3b51d0d4c6f1a10cf","tid":2205002,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee05ceebddc51455d4b18bf1f8d94b382e2be716","tid":2205002,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773779-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773779-PH.jpg&h=68bfc45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲趙秀珍日前分享了隆胸後的成果。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773780-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773780-PH.jpg&h=616665ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773792-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773792-PH.jpg&h=a2af9000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲ 趙秀珍透過影片記錄整型過程。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/15/2773793-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2F2773793-PH.jpg&h=63214fc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28cc91aa33c465a4d2e1fde54aad82c1903c482c","tid":2205002,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T13:02:04.000Z","msg":"果然我老婆係最pure<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0351b341fd5cecd34421563901aa646875a9e2b","tid":2205002,"ui